U_TECHPACK_ALIE.Name: UP_TECH_PACK_ALIEN_NAME
U_TECHPACK_ALIE.Subtitle: UP_TECH_PACK_ALIEN_SUB
U_TECHPACK_ALIE.Description_Text: A cryogenically frozen node, designed to facilitate the archival of bio-technology<> for sentient starships<>. Use FE_ALT1<><> to begin the installation process<>. %TECH_DESC%

F_ALL_LEG_S1.Name: UI_FISH_ALL_LEG_S1_NAME
F_ALL_LEG_S1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_ALL_LEG_S1.Description_Text: "A voice like honey from a mouth of mucus."

F_ALL_LEG_M1.Name: UI_FISH_ALL_LEG_M1_NAME
F_ALL_LEG_M1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_ALL_LEG_M1.Description_Text: "Its tentacles that glitter like wisps of golden hair, but sting with the fire of thousand suns."

F_ALL_LEG_L1.Name: UI_FISH_ALL_LEG_L1_NAME
F_ALL_LEG_L1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_ALL_LEG_L1.Description_Text: "Territorial, ancient, furious to be caught. The king of the sea."

F_ALL_LEG_XL.Name: UI_FISH_ALL_LEG_XL_NAME
F_ALL_LEG_XL.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_ALL_LEG_XL.Description_Text: "A true titan of the depths. Nothing compares for sheer mass."

F_TOX_LEG_S1.Name: UI_FISH_TOX_LEG_S1_NAME
F_TOX_LEG_S1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_TOX_LEG_S1.Description_Text: "Its perfect crystalline form glistens with a emerald light that changes the soul of all those whose eyes fall upon it."

F_TOX_LEG_M1.Name: UI_FISH_TOX_LEG_M1_NAME
F_TOX_LEG_M1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_TOX_LEG_M1.Description_Text: "A true error of the deep; its hungry bite corrupts your blood, filling your body with a spurting corrosive bile."

F_TOX_LEG_L1.Name: UI_FISH_TOX_LEG_L1_NAME
F_TOX_LEG_L1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_TOX_LEG_L1.Description_Text: "Robbed of flesh and stripped of colour by acid seas, the bonefish swims on regardless."

F_TOX_LEG_XL.Name: UI_FISH_TOX_LEG_XL_NAME
F_TOX_LEG_XL.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_TOX_LEG_XL.Description_Text: "Seemingly weak and fragile at the surface, these giant jaws have swallowed alive many an unwary soul who ventured into their abyssal home..."

F_RAD_LEG_S1.Name: UI_FISH_RAD_LEG_S1_NAME
F_RAD_LEG_S1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_RAD_LEG_S1.Description_Text: "A thousand eyes erupt from its soft flesh: a never-ending cycle of rising, blinking, sinking, and re-emergence."

F_RAD_LEG_M1.Name: UI_FISH_RAD_LEG_M1_NAME
F_RAD_LEG_M1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_RAD_LEG_M1.Description_Text: "Its wings beat slowly as it sails though the poisoned seas, a drifter with no place of rest, no end to their journey."

F_RAD_LEG_L1.Name: UI_FISH_RAD_LEG_L1_NAME
F_RAD_LEG_L1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_RAD_LEG_L1.Description_Text: "A pale blue glow surrounds it as it drifts through the water - a warning to all those who would come too close..."

F_RAD_LEG_XL.Name: UI_FISH_RAD_LEG_XL_NAME
F_RAD_LEG_XL.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_RAD_LEG_XL.Description_Text: "Polymorphic, twisting, always in motion; its body a constant whirr of shifting forms and ripping teeth."

F_HOT_LEG_S1.Name: UI_FISH_HOT_LEG_S1_NAME
F_HOT_LEG_S1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_HOT_LEG_S1.Description_Text: "Its glittering shell is practically unbreakable, a material of pure perfection."

F_HOT_LEG_M1.Name: UI_FISH_HOT_LEG_M1_NAME
F_HOT_LEG_M1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_HOT_LEG_M1.Description_Text: "Impossible to see with mortal eyes as it flashes through the water under boiling, cloudless skies."

F_HOT_LEG_L1.Name: UI_FISH_HOT_LEG_L1_NAME
F_HOT_LEG_L1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_HOT_LEG_L1.Description_Text: "A dark cloud follows this creature, and dreams of doom await all those who touch it."

F_HOT_LEG_XL.Name: UI_FISH_HOT_LEG_XL_NAME
F_HOT_LEG_XL.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_HOT_LEG_XL.Description_Text: "Heart of stone and fins of iron, this creature lives on where all else falters."

F_COLD_LEG_S1.Name: UI_FISH_COLD_LEG_S1_NAME
F_COLD_LEG_S1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_COLD_LEG_S1.Description_Text: "A living snowflake: frozen solid yet still alive, its tentacles a fractal recursion."

F_COLD_LEG_M1.Name: UI_FISH_COLD_LEG_M1_NAME
F_COLD_LEG_M1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_COLD_LEG_M1.Description_Text: "A name only spoken in whispers, its pale body a illusion that flickers beneath the moonlit waves."

F_COLD_LEG_L1.Name: UI_FISH_COLD_LEG_L1_NAME
F_COLD_LEG_L1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_COLD_LEG_L1.Description_Text: "A heart that beats but once a hour, a heart that sees faster life spawn and die, spawn and die, spawn and die..."

F_COLD_LEG_XL.Name: UI_FISH_COLD_LEG_XL_NAME
F_COLD_LEG_XL.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_COLD_LEG_XL.Description_Text: "None would believe the scale of this beast: its colossal shell, its enormous slimy foot. None, except those who have seen it..."

F_LUSH_LEG_S1.Name: UI_FISH_LUSH_LEG_S1_NAME
F_LUSH_LEG_S1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_LUSH_LEG_S1.Description_Text: "A creature of dreams, only visible where the light refracts through its soft, perfect jelly."

F_LUSH_LEG_M1.Name: UI_FISH_LUSH_LEG_M1_NAME
F_LUSH_LEG_M1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_LUSH_LEG_M1.Description_Text: "When hunting, can dissolve into a thin dark cloud, impossible to track, impossible to see coming..."

F_LUSH_LEG_L1.Name: UI_FISH_LUSH_LEG_L1_NAME
F_LUSH_LEG_L1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_LUSH_LEG_L1.Description_Text: "A powerful, muscular body and teeth like razors, these gentle giants protect smaller creatures from predators."

F_LUSH_LEG_XL.Name: UI_FISH_LUSH_LEG_XL_NAME
F_LUSH_LEG_XL.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_LUSH_LEG_XL.Description_Text: "The old man of the sea; scarred, blinded, still swimming on..."

F_DUST_LEG_S1.Name: UI_FISH_DUST_LEG_S1_NAME
F_DUST_LEG_S1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_DUST_LEG_S1.Description_Text: "A delicate creature, a fragment of the past that lives on in the water."

F_DUST_LEG_M1.Name: UI_FISH_DUST_LEG_M1_NAME
F_DUST_LEG_M1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_DUST_LEG_M1.Description_Text: "The many-mouths arise from the darkness of the ocean; the many-mouths hunger for their home in the sand..."

F_DUST_LEG_L1.Name: UI_FISH_DUST_LEG_L1_NAME
F_DUST_LEG_L1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_DUST_LEG_L1.Description_Text: "A relic of another age, a fusion of life and stone that refuses to die."

F_DUST_LEG_XL.Name: UI_FISH_DUST_LEG_XL_NAME
F_DUST_LEG_XL.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_DUST_LEG_XL.Description_Text: "The apex of marine predation, a perfect killing machine. Beware."

F_DEEP_LEG_S1.Name: UI_FISH_DEEP_LEG_S1_NAME
F_DEEP_LEG_S1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_DEEP_LEG_S1.Description_Text: "Deep feeling swims in those watery eyestalks, the thoughtful intelligence of a true ancient."

F_DEEP_LEG_M1.Name: UI_FISH_DEEP_LEG_M1_NAME
F_DEEP_LEG_M1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_DEEP_LEG_M1.Description_Text: "It slides beneath the waves; it slides between the ears; it slides within the folds, and swims forever in your dreams."

F_DEEP_LEG_L1.Name: UI_FISH_DEEP_LEG_L1_NAME
F_DEEP_LEG_L1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_DEEP_LEG_L1.Description_Text: "Streamlined, deadly, perfect: the terror of the deep."

F_DEEP_LEG_XL.Name: UI_FISH_DEEP_LEG_XL_NAME
F_DEEP_LEG_XL.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_DEEP_LEG_XL.Description_Text: "So young and fragile, despite its years beneath the waves. And yet thousands more years must pass before it joins the great herd in the stars..."

F_GAS_LEG_S1.Name: UI_FISH_GAS_LEG_S1_NAME
F_GAS_LEG_S1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_GAS_LEG_S1.Description_Text: "The geometry of its impossible body folds within itself, a writhing thread of flesh and spacetime."

F_GAS_LEG_M1.Name: UI_FISH_GAS_LEG_M1_NAME
F_GAS_LEG_M1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_GAS_LEG_M1.Description_Text: "Brilliantly ablaze, its surface a perfect liquid sun..."

F_GAS_LEG_L1.Name: UI_FISH_GAS_LEG_L1_NAME
F_GAS_LEG_L1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_GAS_LEG_L1.Description_Text: "Both alive and not alive; at once a creature, a mineral, and a moment from another time..."

F_GAS_LEG_XL.Name: UI_FISH_GAS_LEG_XL_NAME
F_GAS_LEG_XL.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_GAS_LEG_XL.Description_Text: "So few things survive in waters such as these... so that which thrives should strike fear into the heart of any thinking being."

F_ODD_LEG_S1.Name: UI_FISH_ODD_LEG_S1_NAME
F_ODD_LEG_S1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_ODD_LEG_S1.Description_Text: "Listen to these words: Do not allow this egg to hatch. Cast it back into the sea."

F_ODD_LEG_M1.Name: UI_FISH_ODD_LEG_M1_NAME
F_ODD_LEG_M1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_ODD_LEG_M1.Description_Text: "Shell and claw of perfect crystal, eyestalks aglow with purple rage; a being displaced from another reality and cast here as crab."

F_ODD_LEG_L1.Name: UI_FISH_ODD_LEG_L1_NAME
F_ODD_LEG_L1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_ODD_LEG_L1.Description_Text: "Its song resonates across time and space, calling to its home in the endless black above. One day, it will rise and return to its home among the stars."

F_ODD_LEG_XL.Name: UI_FISH_ODD_LEG_XL_NAME
F_ODD_LEG_XL.Subtitle: UI_FISH_LEGEND_SUB
F_ODD_LEG_XL.Description_Text: "On the surface or below the waves, the vessel hungers, the vessel feeds..."

F_TRASH_1.Name: UI_FISH_TRASH_WEED1_NAME
F_TRASH_1.Subtitle: UI_FISH_TRASH_SUB
F_TRASH_1.Description_Text:
A piece of flotsam, wrenched from its years of drifting in the water when it became entangled in a fishing lure.

Of little use to anyone.

F_TRASH_7.Name: UI_FISH_TRASH_BOOT_NAME
F_TRASH_7.Subtitle: UI_FISH_TRASH_SUB
F_TRASH_7.Description_Text:
A piece of flotsam, wrenched from its years of drifting in the water when it became entangled in a fishing lure.

Of little use to anyone.

F_TRASH_8.Name: UI_FISH_TRASH_METAL_NAME
F_TRASH_8.Subtitle: UI_FISH_TRASH_SUB
F_TRASH_8.Description_Text: A technology upgrade that has been permanently damaged<> by prolonged exposure to water. Use FE_ALT1<><> to begin upgrade installation process<>.

F_BOTTLE.Name: UI_FISH_TRASH_BOTTLE_NAME
F_BOTTLE.Subtitle: UI_FISH_TRASH_SUB
F_BOTTLE.Description_Text: A sealed bottle, found floating in the water. There appears to be a message inside. Use FE_ALT1<><> to unseal<> the bottle and read the message within.

F_JELLYCHILD.Name: UI_FISH_JELLYCHILD_NAME
F_JELLYCHILD.Subtitle: UI_FISH_JELLYCHILD_SUB
F_JELLYCHILD.Description_Text:
An impossibly delicate jellyfish. Its tentacles are as fine as strands of hair, its entire being glassy, dancing on the edge of what is possible.

A gift from the sea, almost too precious to keep...

BAIT_BASIC.Name: BAIT_BASIC_NAME
BAIT_BASIC.Subtitle: BAIT_BASIC_SUB
BAIT_BASIC.Description_Text: Basic creature bait<>. Can be placed directly or accessed via the Quick Menu (QUICK_MENU<>). This bait will attract creatures and cause them to yield Faecium<>. Once a creature has been fed, they may be tamed<> or farmed<> for their produce. Dropping bait may calm angry<> creatures.

BAIT_MEAT_1.Name: BAIT_MEAT_1_NAME
BAIT_MEAT_1.Subtitle: BAIT_MEAT_SUB
BAIT_MEAT_1.Description_Text: A specialist bait<> for carnivores<>. Use the Analysis Visor<> to discover the bait preferences of specific creatures. Created in a Nutrient Processor<> from Mordite<> and assorted creature flesh<>. Feeding using the correct bait will allow creatures to be ridden<> or harvested<>. It will also calm predators<>. Chose bait type from the Quick Menu (QUICK_MENU<>).

BAIT_MEAT_2.Name: BAIT_MEAT_2_NAME
BAIT_MEAT_2.Subtitle: BAIT_MEAT_SUB
BAIT_MEAT_2.Description_Text: A specialist bait<> for carnivores<>. Use the Analysis Visor<> to discover the bait preferences of specific creatures. Created in a Nutrient Processor<> from Mordite<> and assorted creature flesh<>. Feeding using the correct bait will allow creatures to be ridden<> or harvested<>. It will also calm predators<>. Chose bait type from the Quick Menu (QUICK_MENU<>).

BAIT_MEAT_3.Name: BAIT_MEAT_3_NAME
BAIT_MEAT_3.Subtitle: BAIT_MEAT_SUB
BAIT_MEAT_3.Description_Text: A specialist bait<> for carnivores<>. Use the Analysis Visor<> to discover the bait preferences of specific creatures. Created in a Nutrient Processor<> from Mordite<> and other scented bait<>. Feeding using the correct bait will allow creatures to be ridden<> or harvested<>. It will also calm predators<>. Chose bait type from the Quick Menu (QUICK_MENU<>).

BAIT_MEAT_4.Name: BAIT_MEAT_4_NAME
BAIT_MEAT_4.Subtitle: BAIT_MEAT_SUB
BAIT_MEAT_4.Description_Text: A specialist bait<> for carnivores<>. Use the Analysis Visor<> to discover the bait preferences of specific creatures. Created in a Nutrient Processor<> from Mordite<> and assorted creature flesh<>. Feeding using the correct bait will allow creatures to be ridden<> or harvested<>. It will also calm predators<>. Chose bait type from the Quick Menu (QUICK_MENU<>).

BAIT_VEG_1.Name: BAIT_VEG_1_NAME
BAIT_VEG_1.Subtitle: BAIT_VEG_SUB
BAIT_VEG_1.Description_Text: A specialist bait<> for herbivores<>. Use the Analysis Visor<> to discover the bait preferences of specific creatures. Created in a Nutrient Processor<> from Faecium<> and harvestable plants<>. Can be further processed in the Nutrient Processor<> to create new bait types<>. Feeding using the correct bait will allow creatures to be ridden<> or harvested<>. Chose bait type from the Quick Menu (QUICK_MENU<>).

BAIT_VEG_2.Name: BAIT_VEG_2_NAME
BAIT_VEG_2.Subtitle: BAIT_VEG_SUB
BAIT_VEG_2.Description_Text: A specialist bait<> for herbivores<>. Use the Analysis Visor<> to discover the bait preferences of specific creatures. Created in a Nutrient Processor<> from Faecium<> and harvestable plants<>. Can be further processed in the Nutrient Processor<> to create new bait types<>. Feeding using the correct bait will allow creatures to be ridden<> or harvested<>. Chose bait type from the Quick Menu (QUICK_MENU<>).

FUELPROD3.Name: UI_FUELPROD3_NAME
FUELPROD3.Subtitle: UI_FUELPROD3_SUB
FUELPROD3.Description_Text:
Hyper-compressed <FUEL>carbon<>, this substance's dense nanostructure makes it highly valuable as both an energy source and a technology component.

Synthesised from <FUEL>Condensed Carbon<>.

LANDPROD3.Name: UI_LANDPROD3_NAME
LANDPROD3.Subtitle: UI_LANDPROD3_SUB
LANDPROD3.Description_Text:
A highly-prized metal product, this rare element is used in the manufacture of several advanced technologies.

Metal is highly reactive and quickly bonds to exposed skin. User is advised to handle with extreme caution.

Synthesised from <EARTH>Magnetised Ferrite<>.

CAVEPROD3.Name: UI_CAVEPROD3_NAME
CAVEPROD3.Subtitle: UI_CAVEPROD3_SUB
CAVEPROD3.Description_Text:
A novel molecular form of <TECHNOLOGY>Cobalt<>, requiring very high energy levels to create. Natural occurrence is extremely rare.

Synthesised from <TECHNOLOGY>Ionised Cobalt<>.

WATERPROD3.Name: UI_CATAPROD3_NAME
WATERPROD3.Subtitle: UI_CATAPROD3_SUB
WATERPROD3.Description_Text:
A tightly-bonded form of Chlorine. Rigidly-packed molecules offer unrivalled conductivity. Not known to form spontaneously: creation requires highly-focused energy inputs.

Synthesised from <CATALYST>Chlorine<>.

CATAPROD3.Name: UI_WATERPROD3_NAME
CATAPROD3.Subtitle: UI_WATERPROD3_SUB
CATAPROD3.Description_Text:
Sodium is typically highly stable, but certain configurations retain the reactivity of its component ions. User is advised to wear <TECHNOLOGY>Hazardous Material Gauntlets<> before handling.

Synthesised from <TRADEABLE>Sodium<>.

OXYPROD3.Name: UI_OXYPROD3_NAME
OXYPROD3.Subtitle: UI_OXYPROD3_SUB
OXYPROD3.Description_Text:
A para-magnetic form of Oxygen, this rare substance has much to offer in the production of <TECHNOLOGY>advanced technologies<>. Requires conversion prior to input into Life Support systems. Direct inhalation is NOT recommended.

Synthesised from <FUEL>Oxygen<>.

OXY_CRAFT.Name: UI_OXY_CRAFT_NAME
OXY_CRAFT.Subtitle: CRAFTPROD_SUB
OXY_CRAFT.Description_Text:
A specialist technology component.

This small device can rapidly change the gaseous environment within a device, handling conditions from total vacuum to pure oxygen atmospheres.

WATER_CRAFT.Name: UI_WATER_CRAFT_NAME
WATER_CRAFT.Subtitle: CRAFTPROD_SUB
WATER_CRAFT.Description_Text:
A specialist technology component, vital to the complex internals of modern laser systems. 

This light-scattering device takes advantage of the unique optical properties of stabilised and polished salt, to both slow and refract passing photons.

CAVE_CRAFT.Name: UI_CAVE_CRAFT_NAME
CAVE_CRAFT.Subtitle: CRAFTPROD_SUB
CAVE_CRAFT.Description_Text:
A specialist optical component.

Employing a polished cobalt surface, this mirror is able to selectively filter different wavelengths of light, changing its reflective pattern based on nearby magnetic fields.

CATA_CRAFT.Name: UI_CATA_CRAFT_NAME
CATA_CRAFT.Subtitle: CRAFTPROD_SUB
CATA_CRAFT.Description_Text:
An advanced circuit component.

The refined sodium electrode within its vacuum tube gives this diode specialist surge-protection capabilities.

PRODFUEL1.Name: FUELGEL_NAME
PRODFUEL1.Subtitle: FUELGEL_SUB
PRODFUEL1.Description_Text:
Stablised and secure <FUEL>life support<> filtration gas.

Easily assembled from <FUEL>Oxygen<> and <EARTH>Ferrite Dust<>. Offers an efficient method for long-term life support power.

POWERCELL2.Name: POWERCELL2_NAME
POWERCELL2.Subtitle: POWERPROD_SUB
POWERCELL2.Description_Text:
Powerful energy storage unit. Used in a wide variety of <COMMODITY>defensive<> and <COMMODITY>hazard protection<> systems.

Constructed from <TECHNOLOGY>Ionised Cobalt<> and <EARTH>Pure Ferrite<>, and occasionally found in cylindrical metal containers.
